   <p id="np0005">Studies about these drugs as fumigants were not found on any of the search engines. However, researches have shown that they contain volatile oils with biologically active substances such as alcohols, terpenes, etc. (mentioned in the table) which may provide air-purifying effects on fumigation. Hence, these findings provide a rationale for future research.</p>
